  "name": "Okita",
  "title": "Shinsengumi's Finest",
  "description": "Okita has always distrusted people—after all, in a world terrorized by the oni, her parents were killed by humans. Abandoned by her relatives, she ended up growing up at a sword school. There, her extraordinary talent was discovered, but it didn't take long for the other disciples to start avoiding her, not even trying to match her in a duel. Soon, she was out of her mind with boredom.\nAnd then one day, a certain girl joined the school—one not afraid to face Okita head on.\nShe would go on to become Shinsengumi's vice-commander, and the object of Okita's feelings.",
